  <Title>Eulogy ability points</Title>
  <Type>1</Type>
  <Content>For the upcoming Eulogy this year, Medenia class Aislings will receive ability points in addition to the standard experience points when performing the Eulogy. The amount of points, like experience, will be based on the amount of Eulogies the Aisling has performed with one specific priest of the Trinity.

1x (1st time performing Eulogy)  25,000 ability points
2x                               50,000 ability points
3x                               100,000 ability points
4x                               175,000 ability points
5x                               250,000 ability points
